
STEPS
=====

vagrant up

vagrant ssh

sudo /etc/init.d/tomcat start
sudo nginx -s reload



TESTING
=======

Add this to your /etc/hosts:
127.0.0.1       www.sandbox.local sandbox.local app1.sandbox.local



Nginx:
http://app1.sandbox.local:4567/

Tomcat:
http://app1.sandbox.local:4568/index.jsp

Nginx + Tomcat:
http://app1.sandbox.local:4567/index.jsp



RESOURCES
=========

